    <description><![CDATA[<strong>GPXTrackMap 2 - Version 2.0.1</strong><br /><br />GPXTrackMap 2 is a plugin to display GPX tracks on OpenStreetMap maps in articles using the OpenLayers library.<br /><br /><em>Basic Usage:</em><br /><br />{gpxtrackmap}track.gpx{/gpxtrackmap}<br /><br />Please enable the plugin after installation, then set the options as required.]]></description>

